Figure 5 Contrast separation by changing the WD. (a) Sketch drawing of the 
trajectories of LA and HA in the Zeiss GEMINI system as a function of WD. (b-d) LVSEM 
images of polymer-sorted CNT array obtained by the Inlens detector with WDs of (b) 1, (c) 
3, and (d) 5 mm. The insets show the corresponding schematic illustrations of the SEM 
images. Scale bar: 100 nm
